<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>Your privacy is important to us at MyCat. This site is designed to help you manage your beloved cat pets with ease and care.</p>

<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
<p>We only collect information that you voluntarily provide when adding or managing your cat profiles, such as names, age, breed, and other details about your cats.</p>

<h3>How We Use Your Information</h3>
<p>All the information you provide is stored locally in our database and is used solely to improve your experience managing your cats on this site.</p>

<h3>Data Security</h3>
<p>We take reasonable measures to protect your data, but please be aware that no system is completely secure.</p>

<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
<p>MyCat does not share your data with any third-party services.</p>

<h3>Cookies</h3>
<p>We do not use cookies to track you or your activities on this site.</p>

<h3>Contact Us</h3>
<p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@mycat.com">contact@mycat.com</a>.</p>
